      "text": "Intake manifold removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Intake manifold development"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583033_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Air cleaner removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000413",
          "label": "Air cleaner removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Intercooler removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000418",
          "label": "Intercooler removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Throttle body removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R002172",
          "label": "Throttle body removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Do not disconnect the water bypass hose."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Intake manifold stay removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583034_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Tube/Coupler Disconnect"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583035_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A). Disconnect purge tube (B), relief tube (C), PCV tube (D) and master power tube (E)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Intake manifold removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583036_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the harness holder (A). Remove the intake manifold (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Refer to the development diagram when removing the addition."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Intake manifold installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583037_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install the intake manifold (B) using new gaskets (A). Install the harness holder (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "When tightening the intake manifold mounting bolts, tighten them several times diagonally from inside to outside.",
        "Refer to the development drawing when installing add-ons."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Tube/Coupler Connection"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583038_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Connect the master power tube (A), PCV tube (B), relief tube (C) and purge tube (D). Connect the coupler (E)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Intake manifold stay installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "415_3.0_jpn_11583039_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Tighten the intake manifold stay mounting bolts in order of number."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Throttle Body Mounting",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R002172",
          "label": "Throttle Body Mounting",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Intercooler installation",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000418",
          "label": "Intercooler installation",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Air Cleaner Installation",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000413",
          "label": "Air Cleaner Installation",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
